## **Capstone Project Options (Choose One):**

1. **"Comprehensive Farm Performance & Profitability System"**
   - Multi-farm production and economic analysis
   - Crop profitability comparison and optimization
   - Farm management recommendations

2. **"Agricultural Market Intelligence Platform"**
   - Price forecasting and market trends
   - Value chain markup analysis
   - Trading opportunity identification

3. **"Food Security Early Warning System"**
   - Regional food security monitoring
   - Vulnerability and risk assessment
   - Intervention prioritization framework

4. **"Climate-Smart Agriculture Decision Support Tool"**
   - Weather-yield correlation analysis
   - Climate risk assessment
   - Adaptation strategy recommendations

5. **"Agricultural Supply Chain Optimization Analysis"**
   - Post-harvest loss reduction strategies
   - Logistics and transportation optimization
   - Storage and distribution efficiency

6. **"Precision Agriculture ROI Analysis"**
   - Technology adoption feasibility
   - Cost-benefit analysis of smart farming
   - Implementation roadmap

7. **"Custom Project with Real Partner"** (If available)
   - Work with actual agribusiness, NGO, or Ministry
   - Real-world data and business problem
   - Deliverable for potential implementation

